Title: Add global option to log logon failures
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1622637653
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

With this option you can enable the logging of logon failures. If enabled, the
username and client the request is comming from is logged to ~/var/log/web.log.
